strings.Value: "We are running short of supplies. I hope there are people in this party ready to hunt â€” or ready to go without food until we replenish our stocks."
"Our supplies are running low. Either we find a way to replenish our provisions, or we'll have to tighten our belts."
"Oh, I can do without food for a long time! Sometimes no one fed us slaves for several days in a row!"
"It's no fun with no chow. We should bring more next time."
"The food will come. By the hunt or by trade."
"The general speaks the truth. A few more days, and we'll be drinking pine bark soup."
